member.summary:
           Provides add-edit-delete-get process json files that hold one list.


Default CultureInfo is en-US 

Default Encoding is UTF8 


Example json file template for use this library methods; 



Structure 1 :

            "connectionstring"


Structure 2 :
           [
            {
              "Id": 1,
              "Name": "poco1",
              "Which": false
            },
            {
              "Id": 2,
              "Name": "poco2",
              "Which": true
            },
            {
              "Id": 3,
              "Name": "poco3",
              "Which": true
            }
           ]


Structure 3 :

            {
              "Id": 1,
              "Name": "poco1",
              "Which": false
            },
            {
              "Id": 2,
              "Name": "poco2",
              "Which": true
            },
